para_trans: Post promotion to the post of Deputy Secretary
GOVERNMENT ORDER NUMBER: SASB 1125 / P.No.64 / PRASHT 1
Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,
Reference: - General Administration Department, Government Order No: SASB 1125 / Q. No. 64 / Pr. 1, D. 09.06.2025
Smt. Nita Eknath Shinde has been transferred from the rank of Under Secretary to the rank of Deputy Secretary by an order in this regard.
He was promoted and posted to the Home Department after his promotion.
2. Now under this order, after the promotion of Smt. Nita Eknath Shinde to the post of Deputy Secretary,
The posting is being partially changed and revised post promotion to the post of Deputy Secretary.
The post is being posted in the General Administration Department.
3. The terms and conditions of promotion of Smt. Nita Eknath Shinde as mentioned in the order in question.
This Government Order is published on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
